  			<h5>Executive Director</h5>
  			<p>David is the Executive Director of <a href="http://participatorypolitics.org/">PPF</a> and has served as Program Manager of OpenCongress since its launch in 2007. Previously, he worked as the first Outreach Coordinator for <a href="http://pculture.org/">PCF</a>, where he helped to launch <a href="http://getmiro.com/">Miro</a>. David spends a decent amount of time following the Milwaukee Brewers. He lives in Brooklyn, NY.</p>
