  			<h5>Lead Programmer</h5>
  			<p>Andy Ross is the Lead Programmer of OpenCongress and has coded on it since development started in 2006. Andy maintains the core data streams that form OpenCongress and builds the site's open-source Ruby on Rails code. A dedicated fan of the Boston Red Sox, he lives in Los Angeles, CA.</p>
  			<p><i>Contact: aross[at]opencongress.org</i></p>
